Disabled locally: this test depends on an external yojson package built for the
same compiler as MERLIN_TEST_OCAML_PATH. The current harness can combine the
OxCaml compiler from MERLIN_TEST_OCAML_PATH with yojson from the ambient opam
switch, producing a wrong-CMI-magic failure unrelated to Merlin behavior.

  $ cat >dune-project <<'EOF'
  > (lang dune 3.0)
  > EOF

  $ cat >dune <<'EOF'
  > (executable (name foo))
  > (executable (name foobar) (libraries yojson))
  > EOF

  $ touch foo.ml 

  $ cat >foobar.ml <<'EOF'
  > let eq = Yojson.equal
  > let () = Printf.printf "%b" @@ eq `Null `Null
  > EOF

  $ $DUNE build 
  $ $DUNE exec ./foobar.exe
  true

